text:
NeNe Leakes is standing her ground. There was some more beef between the Real Housewives of Atlanta star and her co-star Porsha Williamsabout some unfiltered remarks Leakes dished on Watch What Happens Live With Andy Cohen in May.

Read more: http://www.eonline.com/news/891815/nene-leakes-denies-saying-porsha-williams-should-be-fired
title: NeNe Leakes Denies Saying Porsha Williams Should Be Fired
